---
title: One-Pot Southwest Double Beef and Cavatappi with Monterey Jack and Baby Spinach
description: This one-and-done dinner-in-a-hurry packs beef, veggies and pasta into one easy bowl. The best part? It's a meal everyone is sure to devour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1014_W17_CA_RB152752-6__11low-30a2e098.jpg
